### Apply migrations to all tenants (Product Owner only)
POST {{host}}/api/admin/apply-migrations
Authorization: Bearer {{productOwnerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Apply migrations to specific tenant (Product Owner only)
POST {{host}}/api/admin/apply-migrations/tenant-abc
Authorization: Bearer {{productOwnerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantIdentifier": "tenant-abc"
}

###

### Variables for testing
@host = https://localhost:7253
@productOwnerToken = your-product-owner-jwt-token-here

